**Gross Profit Margin (September 29 2024)**  

\[
\text{Gross Profit Margin} = \frac{\text{Revenue} - \text{COGS}}{\text{Revenue}}
= \frac{38{,}962 - 17{,}060}{38{,}962}
= \frac{21{,}902}{38{,}962}
\approx 0.5625 \; (\text{or } 56.3\%)
\]

**Answer:** **≈ 56.3 %**.

**Average Accounts Receivable**

\[
\frac{\text{Accounts Receivable}_{2024} + \text{Accounts Receivable}_{2023}}{2}
= \frac{3{,}929 + 3{,}183}{2}
= \frac{7{,}112}{2}
= 3{,}556
\]

**Result:** **$3,556** (in the same monetary units used in the table).

**Average Accounts Payable**

\[
\frac{\text{Trade accounts payable (2024)} + \text{Trade accounts payable (2023)}}{2}
= \frac{2{,}584 + 1{,}912}{2}
= \frac{4{,}496}{2}
= 2{,}248
\]

**Result:** **$2,248** (in the same monetary units used in the table).

**Average Net Fixed Assets**  

\[
\frac{\text{Net Fixed Assets}_{2024} + \text{Net Fixed Assets}_{2023}}{2}
= \frac{4{,}665 + 5{,}042}{2}
= \frac{9{,}707}{2}
= 4{,}853.5
\]

**Result:** **$4,853.5** (in the same monetary units used in the table).
